 messages buried the real error in the console output until Mina filtered the logs.","sentence_zh":"大量调试消息一直把真正的错误掩盖在控制台输出中，直到米娜筛选了日志。","add_node_ids":["filter","mina","logs"],"add_link_ids":["filter->mina","filter->logs","filter->bury"],"focus_node_id":"filter","note_zh":"日志筛选标志着错误不再被噪声掩盖。"}]}'
